ed `replaced_by: GO:0008290`\n+\n+Validation:\n+\n+- Pre-validation: `robot convert -i go-edit.obo -f obo -o /tmp/opencode/go-edit.prevalidate.obo`\n+- Full validation: `cd src/ontology && make travis_build`\n+- Result: passed\n+\n+Checklist:\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: Issue context reviewed and intent was clear\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Local ontology syntax checked before edits\n+- [N/A] RESEARCH: No new biological content or references introduced\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Confirmed `GO:0005870` and replacement `GO:0008290` in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [N/A] DESIGN-PATTERNS: No new logical definitions added\n+- [x] EDITS: Used `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` with `terms/GO_0005870.obo`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: Removed obsolete logical axioms as required for obsoletion\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: Applied `/term-obsoletion` workflow\n+- [x] METADATA: Added obsoletion metadata and tracker link; did not add creation metadata to an existing term\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed\n+- [N/A] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: No new references added\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: Local commit created for `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` only\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,5 @@\n+Addressed in local commit `89f53af` and ready for PR submission as PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Obsoleted `GO:0005870` (`actin capping protein of dynactin complex`) with direct replacement to `GO:0008290` (`F-actin capping protein complex`), following the request in this issue.\n+\n+I also checked for ontology-internal references and direct annotations before obsoleting the term; none turned up in local checks. Full ontology validation passed with `make travis_build`.\n\n